test.title: Document has an instrument to move focus to non-repeated content
test.description: This rule checks that there is an instrument to move focus to non-repeated content in the page.

result.description: The page has one or more instrument(s) to move focus. Check if any of these instrument(s) is being used before a block of repeated content, and the focus is moved to just before a block of non-repeated content.
